@startuml
'https://plantuml.com/sequence-diagram
!pragma layout smetana

autonumber

actor "User" as User
participant "RestClient" as RC
box "Smart Home"
    participant "Backend" as BE
end box



User -> RC : I want to deactivate a device
activate RC

RC -> BE : deactivateDevice(deviceId)
activate BE

BE --> RC : deviceDTO
deactivate BE

RC --> User : deviceDTO
deactivate RC
@enduml